&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( brothers ) is a 1970 bollywood suspense drama film directed by raja &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it had music by shankar &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; with lyrics by hasrat jaipuri . the film stars sunil dutt , asha parekh , mumtaz , mehmood and pran . it performed " above average " at the box office . the story revolves around sunil dutt , playing the role of a writer , whose character from his story seemingly comes to life killing people . this puts him under suspicion from the police . the film had sunil dutt in a double role .